Package: mc-server
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Dylan Bulmer <dylan@bulmer.dev>
Depends: curl, jq
Recommends: rsync, mc-rcon
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://apt.bulmer.dev
Description: Minecraft server lifecycle manager
 mc-server manages a Minecraft server instance on bare-metal or inside VMs/LXC
 containers. It supports Paper, Vanilla, and Fabric server types and provides
 commands for installation, updates, backups, restores, and systemd lifecycle
 management.
 .
 Requires Java 17+ (Java 21 recommended for Minecraft 1.20.5+).
 .
 Install mc-rcon to add the 'mc rcon' subcommand for RCON console access.
